select.id: get高額合算計算結果連絡票情報

mapper.select:
SELECT
FROM( SELECT "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka".*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."hihokenshaNo", "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."taishoNendo", "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."shoKisaiHokenshaNo", "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" ORDER BY "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."rirekiNo" DESC ) AS rowNum FROM rgdb."DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka" AS "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka" WHERE "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."dataKubun" IN ('2', '3') AND "DbT3072KogakuGassanShikyuGakuKeisanKekka"."isDeleted" = FALSE ) AS "計算結果" WHERE "計算結果".rowNum = 1 AND "計算結果"."dataKubun" = '2' AND "計算結果"."hokenSeidoCode" = '3'
AND ("計算結果"."sofuYM" = '' OR "計算結果"."sofuYM" is null OR "計算結果"."sofuYM" = #{処理年月} OR "計算結果"."saisoFG" = '1')
AND ("計算結果"."sofuYM" = '' OR "計算結果"."sofuYM" is null OR "計算結果"."saisoFG" = '1')
ORDER BY "計算結果"."hihokenshaNo", "計算結果"."taishoNendo", "計算結果"."shoKisaiHokenshaNo", "計算結果"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo", "計算結果"."rirekiNo"
